{"tid":253604,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我個fd好姣 我可以點？","createTime":"2017-05-22T13:52:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-22T13:58:52.000Z","uid":54961,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8b566233ce94299861942a658c56264f302590a4","tid":253604,"uid":54961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T13:52:25.000Z","msg":"我有個朋友 <br />\n交代一下佢既背景先<br />\n佢係女黎 識左六年啦    正常樣既普通女仔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地一個月前都好好好好fd<br />\n<br />\n係前排 佢對我態度全部唔同曬<br />\n反而對佢d男同事 又嗲 又唉身唉世<br />\n仲比我見到佢用隻腳(new)聲稱係朋友既男同事隻腳<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過有一日  我就約左佢出街<br />\n不過佢遲左半個鐘<br />\n我問返佢<br />\n原來佢係office同佢班兵吹水 <br />\n唔記得左<br />\n之後我就嬲 走左<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而加對條女越來越反感 <br />\n我覺得你對人好 人地都會對返你好<br />\n但係佢教我既係<br />\n只係拎著數先對人好<br />\n冇著數就係咁先<br />\n<br />\n我之後就同另一個best friend 講啦<br />\n點知個姣婆係到扮可憐 <br />\n話我屈9佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我應該點做？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  絕交啦仲忍<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  明顯樓主問題"},{"pid":"f0df58debdbf2b5fff048eff1fb71cec8cfe6641","tid":253604,"uid":54961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T13:53:08.000Z","msg":"利申藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9e189613454c6f35f6cba2aa4904498dea88070","tid":253604,"uid":61832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T13:54:44.000Z","msg":"唔抵得人地收到兵自己收唔到？"},{"pid":"f44cc0740c85e65f4f3262654ae8012f37fe595a","tid":253604,"uid":83553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T13:55:21.000Z","msg":"你幾歲"},{"pid":"4921